### Positive test: User can open deposit money page
UI
Login as user
Open User Dashboard
Click Deposit Money button
Check Deposit Money page is opened
Check Select Account dropdown is displayed
Check Enter Amount field is displayed
Check Deposit button is displayed

### Positive test: User can deposit money to own existing account
UI
Login as user
Open User Dashboard
Click Deposit Money button
Select own account
Enter amount "200.00"
Click Deposit button
Check success message is displayed
Check account balance is increased by 200.00
Check account balance is increased by 200.00 via API
Check deposit transaction is created via API

### Positive test: User can deposit maximum allowed amount
UI
Login as user
Open User Dashboard
Click Deposit Money button
Select own account
Enter amount "5000.00"
Click Deposit button
Check success message is displayed
Check account balance is increased by 5000.00
Check account balance is increased by 5000.00 via API

### Negative test: User can not deposit amount greater than maximum allowed amount
UI
Login as user
Open User Dashboard
Click Deposit Money button
Select own account
Enter amount "5000.01"
Click Deposit button
Check validation error is displayed
Check account balance is not changed
Check account balance is not changed via API

### Negative test: User can not submit deposit without selected account
UI
Login as user
Open User Dashboard
Click Deposit Money button
Leave account dropdown empty
Enter amount "200.00"
Click Deposit button
Check validation error is displayed
Check deposit is not completed

### Negative test: User can not submit deposit with blank amount
UI
Login as user
Open User Dashboard
Click Deposit Money button
Select own account
Leave amount field blank
Click Deposit button
Check validation error is displayed
Check account balance is not changed

### Positive test: User can open transfer page
UI
Login as user
Open User Dashboard
Click Make a Transfer button
Check Make a Transfer page is opened
Check Select Your Account dropdown is displayed
Check Recipient Name field is displayed
Check Recipient Account Number field is displayed
Check Amount field is displayed
Check Confirm details are correct checkbox is displayed
Check Send Transfer button is displayed

### Positive test: User can transfer money with valid amount
UI
Login as user
Open User Dashboard
Click Make a Transfer button
Select sender account
Enter recipient name
Enter recipient account number
Enter amount "100.00"
Check Confirm details are correct checkbox
Click Send Transfer button
Check success message is displayed
Check sender account balance is decreased by 100.00
Check receiver account balance is increased by 100.00
Check sender account balance is decreased by 100.00 via API
Check receiver account balance is increased by 100.00 via API
Check transfer transaction is created via API

### Positive test: User can transfer maximum allowed amount
UI
Login as user
Open User Dashboard
Click Make a Transfer button
Select sender account
Enter recipient name
Enter recipient account number
Enter amount "10000.00"
Check Confirm details are correct checkbox
Click Send Transfer button
Check success message is displayed
Check sender account balance is decreased by 10000.00
Check receiver account balance is increased by 10000.00
Check sender and receiver balances are changed via API

### Negative test: User can not transfer amount greater than maximum allowed amount
UI
Login as user
Open User Dashboard
Click Make a Transfer button
Select sender account
Enter recipient name
Enter recipient account number
Enter amount "10000.01"
Check Confirm details are correct checkbox
Click Send Transfer button
Check validation error is displayed
Check sender account balance is not changed
Check receiver account balance is not changed
Check sender and receiver balances are not changed via API

### Negative test: User can not transfer amount greater than sender account balance
UI
Login as user
Open User Dashboard
Click Make a Transfer button
Select sender account with balance 500.00
Enter recipient name
Enter recipient account number
Enter amount "1000.00"
Check Confirm details are correct checkbox
Click Send Transfer button
Check error message is displayed
Check sender account balance is not changed
Check receiver account balance is not changed
Check sender and receiver balances are not changed via API

### Negative test: User can not submit transfer without selected sender account
UI
Login as user
Open User Dashboard
Click Make a Transfer button
Leave sender account dropdown empty
Enter recipient name
Enter recipient account number
Enter amount "100.00"
Check Confirm details are correct checkbox
Click Send Transfer button
Check validation error is displayed
Check transfer is not completed

### Negative test: User can not submit transfer without recipient account number
UI
Login as user
Open User Dashboard
Click Make a Transfer button
Select sender account
Enter recipient name
Leave recipient account number field blank
Enter amount "100.00"
Check Confirm details are correct checkbox
Click Send Transfer button
Check validation error is displayed
Check transfer is not completed

### Negative test: User can not submit transfer without confirmation checkbox
UI
Login as user
Open User Dashboard
Click Make a Transfer button
Select sender account
Enter recipient name
Enter recipient account number
Enter amount "100.00"
Leave Confirm details are correct checkbox unchecked
Click Send Transfer button
Check validation error is displayed
Check transfer is not completed

### Positive test: User can change profile name to valid name
UI
Login as user
Open profile page
Enter name "John Smith"
Click Save button
Check success message is displayed
Check profile name is changed to "John Smith"
Check profile name is changed to "John Smith" via API

### Negative test: User can not change profile name with invalid format
UI
Login as user
Open profile page
Enter name "John Smith1"
Click Save button
Check validation error is displayed
Check old profile name is still displayed
Check profile name is not changed via API